{"id": "1224606564707733567", "channel_id": "1224606564707733567", "type": 0, "author_id": "733514425847513171", "author_name": "xuan4185", "author_bot": false, "content": "正常來說所有未指名攻擊 全體敵人、隨機敵人、生命值最高／低的敵人，都應該被視為攻擊前排敵人，也是打出卡牌後鎖定的第一個敵人（例如第一支影片打擊會鎖定當時唯一在場的敵人），然而命定之劍的索敵邏輯似乎跟其他的不一樣？", "timestamp": "2024-04-02T06:29:17.116000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🤣", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}, {"emoji": "😆", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1224606565101867018", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20240402_140547.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 1273310, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1224606564707733567/1224606565101867018/Screen_Recording_20240402_140547.mp4?ex=6a00ce7d&is=69ff7cfd&hm=485735d4a01f9b3ac6ac000bbfe55bef59c0a99b3c928d8e730b578dd66c20f0&"}, {"id": "1224606565374623814", "filename": "Screen_Recording_20240402_135343.mp4", "content_type": "video/mp4", "size": 2125548, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1224606564707733567/1224606565374623814/Screen_Recording_20240402_135343.mp4?ex=6a00ce7d&is=69ff7cfd&hm=1b1342154b5a4f6a5263bc6233ba72f45a5fd5d62201517aa8aaadd7b7fd41fa&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1224606564707733567", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」命定之劍bug", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168103141416960"]}
{"id": "1224520502044004434", "channel_id": "1224520502044004434", "type": 0, "author_id": "1185719465984413801", "author_name": "sayakakozuki", "author_bot": false, "content": "pv、预告是能拉高人期待值和增加社区话题的东西。\n\n这次不会又到等到明天中午发pv，半夜1点发预告，后天都要更新了，发那么晚是给谁看呢？", "timestamp": "2024-04-02T00:47:18.178000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1224520502044004434", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」1.3的pv和版本更新预告该发了吧？", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168197425172480"]}
{"id": "1224555847724826685", "channel_id": "1224555847724826685", "type": 0, "author_id": "506429011300450346", "author_name": "yusan10220925", "author_bot": false, "content": "幻夢作為每週活動 應該是讓一週內讓玩家打一到二次把獎勵拿滿才對 \n\n以一個手遊角度來看我感覺哪怕是有減負方案我覺得還是不夠\n\n希望可以將負重的部分轉移成新的日常 而不是讓玩家為了900珠珠每天花快20min 硬打完\n\n新日常可以輕鬆快速為主\n可以是一波打完接一波後接著打每一波打完可以直接吃buff跟造物\n\n\n作為輕度玩家我個人的看法可能有些偏頗 \n但是從開服玩到現在作業感最重的肯定是改動後的幻夢。\n每天都要打 但是都在重複類似的流程\n作業感在快速攀升", "timestamp": "2024-04-02T03:07:45.245000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-04-02T03:27:34.208000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🥹", "emoji_id": null, "count": 2}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1224555847724826685", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅「已回答」讓幻夢變成一週一次並增加可以短時間遊玩的關卡", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "is_thread_starter": true, "thread_tags": ["1181168158678204497"]}
